reviewText:
Beat em' up created by Klei. This thing is some serious thing full of murder, brutality and alcohol. Yes, alcohol. In fact, it acts like medkits. The graphic and animations are beautiful, just pure perfection. And even my wooden PC is able to run it on full graphics!

Pros:
- Perform long and very brutal combos;
- Amazing graphics;
- Hard to beat even on normal;
- Bloody executions;
- Healing alcohol!;
- Coop mode to make sick combos together!

Cons:
- Hard to play on keyboard;
- Some enemies can ber very annoying;
- Not for casuals. Hardcores, be warned.
